8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both JetBrains AI and Pieces share a solid foundation of core features including Code Generation, Debugging, Multi Language, Ide Integration. Where JetBrains AI pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Autocomplete and Refactoring and Test Generation and Documentation, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. \n\nLooking at user ratings, JetBrains AI holds an overall score of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 8/10, while Pieces scores 6/10 overall and 8/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
9:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Pieces comes in at a lower starting price of $0, while JetBrains AI begins at $10/mo. Pieces stands out by offering a free plan, giving you a risk-free way to explore the platform. JetBrains AI requires a paid subscription from the start."}]]}]
